| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3947 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1cd17496-80d0-50a4-9e3b-4b0ebbb45882"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
